        notes: "A member of the Brotherhood Without Banners. Was formerly a horse master at Winterfell under Eddard Stark, and knew Arya as a child there — he recognizes her. He serves as a grounding point for Arya's experience with the Brotherhood. First appears ASOS Arya IV."
